last_episode_to_air.name: A Telenovela
last_episode_to_air.overview: JWOWW's feast of peace is not going as planned; Pauly teaches Nikki the difference between rigatoni and linguini; Mike organizes the next family getaway, but he doesn't know if the baby will arrive before the trip.

name: Jersey Shore: Family Vacation

next_episode_to_air.name: The Big Apple
next_episode_to_air.overview: It's baby number 3 time for Mike and Lauren; Sammi continues her IVF journey; the rest of the gang takeover the Big Apple on a double-decker and the last stop is Vinny's standup show.

overview: The cast of Jersey Shore swore they would always do a vacation together. Now, five years, five kids, three marriages, and who knows how many GTL sessions later, the gang is back together and on vacation in a swanky house in Miami Beach.
tagline: It's the biggest family vacation ever!

episodes.name: What's In the Bag?
episodes.overview: After five years apart, our favorite guidos are reuniting in Miami for a family vacation, but The Situation’s legal issues have put his vacation in jeopardy.

episodes.name: The Ring
episodes.overview: Ronnie and Deena’s unresolved issues resurface, and the family is complete with the arrival of The Situation.

episodes.name: Sunday Vinday
episodes.overview: Ronnie clogs all the toilets in the house, and Nicole and Vinny's past jeopardizes their friendship.

episodes.name: Ron Ron Juice
episodes.overview: A night of Ron-Ron Juice has the whole house on full tilt, and a French girl at the club has Ronnie questioning everything.

episodes.name: About Last Night
episodes.overview: Ronnie is in full on spiral mode after a night of epic bad decisions, and Mike has big news to share.

episodes.name: Meatball Down
episodes.overview: Ronnie has to take responsibility for his actions in the club before his pregnant girlfriend's visit, Vinny searches for the perfect barber, and Deena ruins boys' night out.

episodes.name: Baby Mama Drama
episodes.overview: Ron's pregnant girlfriend Jenn arrives for an awkward visit, and Vinny is in the doghouse after he grabs a stripper at the club.

episodes.name: The Temptation of the Keto Guido
episodes.overview: Snooki gets caught stealing from a stripper, Vinny is feeling tempted and might sin, and Pauly D is looking for love.

episodes.name: Umm, Hello
episodes.overview: While the girls are away, Pauly decides to invite their old roommate Angelina to Miami.

episodes.name: Meatball (Training) Day
episodes.overview: The girls go off on Angelina when she makes a surprise return to Miami, and Meatball Day gets weird.

episodes.name: Angelina Leaves Her Mark!
episodes.overview: Angelina's embarrassing bodily mishap leaves a lasting impression on the roomies when she departs the house, and the gang heads to Bimini, Bahamas.

episodes.name: JWoww vs. The Proposal
episodes.overview: Ronnie is spiraling again, Vinny gets a taste of home, and tension between Mike and JWoww might ruin mike’s proposal.

episodes.name: Future Mrs. Situation?
episodes.overview: Ronnie tries to sort out his feelings for his pregnant girlfriend, and the roommates get the house ready for Mike to propose to Lauren.

episodes.name: The Final Supper
episodes.overview: The roommates' final dinner is filled with fun memories and a huge blowup between Ronnie and Mike, and Pauly D runs into a familiar face while he's working.

episodes.name: It's Complicated
episodes.overview: The gang reunites in Las Vegas to meet Ronnie's baby, but no one knows what to expect when Ronnie's relationship drama gets blasted all over social media.

episodes.name: Oh Canada
episodes.overview: Vinny and Pauly meet a pair of Canadian women, Jenni calls out the roomies for bailing on her Mother's Day videos, and Ronnie's relationship drama continues to unfold.

episodes.name: The Truth About Ronnie
episodes.overview: Ronnie is pushed to the edge when the truth about his family situation comes to light, the gang wins big at the casinos, and Jen turns up unexpectedly at the suite.

episodes.name: Heartbreak Hotel
episodes.overview: Ronnie worries about his baby's well-being when he gets news about Jen, Vinny misses Pauly D while he's out of town, and Angelina shocks the roommates when she pays a visit.

episodes.name: Frenemies
episodes.overview: Angelina aggressively tries to smooth things over with Jenni, and Vinny misses Pauly so much that he carries around a cardboard cutout of him.

episodes.name: The Designation
episodes.overview: As their Las Vegas vacation nears the end, Nicole's very extra friend Joey comes for a visit, Jenni leaves the trip early, and Pauly plans a surprise.

episodes.name: Four Guidos and a Baby
episodes.overview: Nicole and Jenni try to mend their friendship, the guys go baby shopping and revisit the Ronnie and Jen warzone, and Vinny and Pauly make a serious bro-mmitment.

episodes.name: Back to Seaside
episodes.overview: Jenni and Angelina finally bury the hatchet, and the gang takes a nostalgia-filled trip back to Seaside Heights.

episodes.name: Vinny and Angelina: A Love Story
episodes.overview: Back where it all started, the roommates enjoy a night back in their original seaside house, but things get messy when Vinny and Angelina air out old dirty laundry.

episodes.name: What a Drag
episodes.overview: Ronnie makes a surprise appearance at Deena's gender reveal party, and later, everyone heads to Atlantic City for Pauly's DJ gig.

episodes.name: Awkward City
episodes.overview: In Atlantic City, the roommates do their best to support Ronnie and Jen’s relationship while celebrating at Pauly’s birthday gig, and Angelina continues to flirt with Vinny.

episodes.name: Where's the Beach?
episodes.overview: As the roommates head back to the Jersey shore, Ronnie and Nicole cut loose before everyone else arrives, and Angelina gets flirty with Vinny after a fight with her fiance.

episodes.name: Staten Island Smackdown
episodes.overview: Jenni joins Mike for his motivational speech at a rehab facility, Pauly arrives for family dinner, and Angelina pushes Vinny too far in their love-hate relationship.

episodes.name: Jewish Barbie
episodes.overview: Mike competes in a burger-eating contest, Nicole takes a pregnancy test, and history repeats itself when Ronnie gets into hot water (literally) with another woman.

episodes.name: Pork Roll or Taylor Ham?
episodes.overview: The roommates come up with an elaborate scheme to kidnap Deena and bring her to the house, while newly single Ronnie takes time to himself to come to terms with his breakup.

episodes.name: Wallopin’ in Manalapan
episodes.overview: The roommates throw a party with Slip 'N Slides, bounce castles and more, and a night out heats up when a stranger pushes Ronnie to his breaking point.

episodes.name: Ronnie Magro's Series of Unfortunate Events
episodes.overview: A call from home leaves Ronnie worried and everyone else skeptical, and the roommates help Deena honor her father's memory and fight cancer with a fundraiser.

episodes.name: The United States v. The Situation, Pt. 1
episodes.overview: As Mike prepares for both a jail sentencing and his wedding, the ladies take his fiancee Lauren to a wedding dress fitting, and Jenni shuts down discussions about her divorce.

episodes.name: The United States v. The Situation, Pt. 2
episodes.overview: Ronnie claims to have gotten into an altercation in a parking lot, and the roommates gather as Mike receives his criminal sentencing for tax evasion.

episodes.name: Secaucus?!
episodes.overview: Mike gets sentenced to eight months in prison for tax evasion, Ronnie raises eyebrows with a story about getting mugged, and the gang heads to a dude ranch.

episodes.name: Guido Cowboys
episodes.overview: During a trip to upstate New York, Angelina and Deena clash over beds, Ronnie reveals that his girlfriend Jen might be pregnant, and Jenni refuses to discuss her divorce.

episodes.name: Ranchelor Party
episodes.overview: The roommates throw Mike a bachelor party, but the guys and ladies have very different kinds of entertainment in mind, and Ronnie wants Jenni to open up about her divorce.

episodes.name: Not Again
episodes.overview: Ronnie falls into a funk as his relationship drama looms over the group, the guys choreograph a dance for Mike's wedding, and Nicole prepares for The Snooki Shop's opening.

episodes.name: Where's Ronnie?
episodes.overview: Deena gets emotional at her baby shower, Mike and Lauren host their wedding rehearsal dinner, and Ronnie's personal woes create tension with the rest of the group.

episodes.name: Tuxedo Time
episodes.overview: Ahead of Mike and Lauren's wedding, Ronnie opens up to Vinny and Pauly about his relationship problems, and Jenni and Nicole help their daughters prepare for flower girl duty.

episodes.name: The Hitch-uation, Pt. 1
episodes.overview: It's time for Mike and Lauren's wedding, but all eyes are on Ronnie's unpredictable girlfriend Jen when she makes the surprising decision to attend.

episodes.name: The Hitch-uation, Pt. 2
episodes.overview: At Mike and Lauren's wedding reception, the guys prepare for their dance routine, Uncle Nino sends Jenn a message, and Pauly D enlists Rob Base to surprise the newlyweds.

episodes.name: Goodbye Mike
episodes.overview: Mike prepares for his prison sentence, Ron realizes it's time to make changes in his life, Jen's split from Roger goes public, and Deena celebrates the birth of her baby boy.

episodes.name: Thirty Days Later
episodes.overview: A fresh-from-rehab Ronnie reconnects with Vinny and Pauly, Nicole relishes pregnancy eating, and Jenni confronts Angelina and Ronnie for talking about her divorce on camera.

episodes.name: JWoww Gets Her Groove Back
episodes.overview: Ronnie throws a birthday party for his daughter, Pauly and Vinny visit Mike behind bars, and Jenni invites her new 24-year-old boyfriend to Las Vegas to meet the roommates.

episodes.name: Gym, Tan, Strip
episodes.overview: As the roommates arrive in Las Vegas, Vinny is worried his ankle injury will affect his Chippendales gig, Pauly senses a "Ronpage" is looming, and Angelina loses a bet.

episodes.name: Tick. Tick. Tick.
episodes.overview: Vinny prepares for his big stripping debut, Ronnie's constant texting leads everyone to suspect trouble at home, and the group gets some good news from Mike in prison.

episodes.name: Strippendales
episodes.overview: Jenni tries to uncover the truth about Ronnie and Jenn, Pauly plans an epic prank, and Vinny makes his Chippendales debut in front of his roommates and mother.

episodes.name: The Incident at the Strip Club
episodes.overview: The roomies don't know what to expect when Ronnie finds out Jenn joined them at the strip club, and Jenni's boyfriend arrives in Las Vegas.

episodes.name: Millennials
episodes.overview: Deena has an encounter with a judgmental bar patron, and Angelina is bothered when Jenni's new boyfriend pries into her sex life.

episodes.name: Holy Drama
episodes.overview: Pauly celebrates the end of Vinny's Chippendales residency with a feast, and looming drama between Jenni and Angelina threatens to upend the baptism for Deena's son CJ.

episodes.name: 4 Fists. 2 Bottles. 1 Shore House.
episodes.overview: Fingers are pointed, piercings are questioned, and wine bottles are at risk when Nicole and Ronnie get drawn into Jenni and Angelina's feud as Deena tries to play peacekeeper.

episodes.name: Last Night Is Cancelled
episodes.overview: The housemates spend a day at the boardwalk as tensions linger between Angelina, Jenni and Nicole, and the boys try to have a good time without Mike.

episodes.name: Snooki Goes To Washington, Pt. 1
episodes.overview: After Lauren tells the gang that Mike's release from prison is being delayed, the ladies head to the White House to ask for help, while the guys let loose in Jenni's new home.

episodes.name: Snooki Goes To Washington, Pt. 2
episodes.overview: The ladies gang up on Vinny after they return from Washington, D.C., the guys plan an elaborate prank, and the roomies get an update about Mike's release from jail.

episodes.name: Only In Jersey
episodes.overview: While Mike awaits his release from prison, the roommates take Lauren bowling to get her mind off things, and Jenni gets into a screaming match with an ice cream truck driver.

episodes.name: Back to the Jersey Shore
episodes.overview: The roommates reunite as Jenni's custody issues threaten her time in the house, Angelina stresses over planning her wedding, and the roommates await Mike's return.

episodes.name: Psychic Larges
episodes.overview: Nicole invites a psychic medium friend to do everyone's readings, and the roommates celebrate Mike's release from prison with a party at the shore house.

episodes.name: Single J-Woww
episodes.overview: Mike reunites with the gang for the first time since his release from prison, Nicole plans a divorce party for Jenni, and Angelina gets Ronnie's advice on her wedding.

episodes.name: Chicken Cutlets and Ketchup
episodes.overview: Angelina finds herself in hot water with Chris after she invites a guy friend to Jenni's divorce party, and Vinny's mom cooks a feast for Mike.

episodes.name: The Shorefather
episodes.overview: The ladies help Angelina shop for her wedding dress, a backyard calamity leaves Deena inconsolable, and the roommates surprise Mike with a homemade movie about his life.

episodes.name: Prenups and Misdemeanors
episodes.overview: Angelina gets an education on prenups, the ladies dig themselves out of trouble, Mike gives 24 the third degree, and Nicole and Deena surprise Mike with some special visitors.

episodes.name: Unresolved Issues
episodes.overview: Angelina's bachelorette party is jeopardized after the roomies see what really happened between Angelina and Zack in Las Vegas, and Pauly, Vinny and Mike plan a guys' weekend.

episodes.name: Crash The Bachelorette
episodes.overview: Jenni and Angelina clear the air, the guys plot to crash Angelina's bachelorette party in New Orleans, and everyone agrees Vinny is to blame for everything that's gone wrong.

episodes.name: Beignets, Blow-up Dolls and Bridesmaids
episodes.overview: While the guys are in New Orleans to surprise Angelina for her bachelorette party, Mike reprises his role as The Designation, and Ronnie and Mike prep Vinny for Jenni's wrath.

episodes.name: P-Woww
episodes.overview: As things get rowdy at Angelina's bachelorette party in New Orleans, Nicole falls asleep at a bar, and Pauly and newly single Jenni wind up in the same bed.

episodes.name: So That Happened!
episodes.overview: Pauly and Jenni endure an awkward morning after, Mike and Lauren move into their first house together, and Angelina and Chris put the finishing touches on their wedding plans.

episodes.name: Rewriting History
episodes.overview: The roommates toast Angelina at the iconic Jersey Shore house before dropping by the Shore Store to prank Danny, and Jenni, Nicole and Deena write a raunchy wedding speech.

episodes.name: You Had Me at "Um, Hello!"
episodes.overview: As Angelina and Chris's wedding day approaches, Jenni suspects the bride's grandmother put a hex on her, and the guys come up with a special dance to surprise the newlyweds.

episodes.name: The Speech, Pt. 1
episodes.overview: On her big day, Angelina gives bridesmaid gifts to Nicole, Jenni and Deena, Uncle Nino helps Jenni dodge a hex, and the ladies' toast incurs the wrath of the wedding guests.

episodes.name: The Speech, Pt 2
episodes.overview: After Angelina gets upset at Nicole, Jenni and Deena for their toast at her wedding reception, it's up to Vinny, Mike, Pauly and Ronnie to lighten the mood.

episodes.name: The Mediation
episodes.overview: Angelina struggles to forgive the ladies after their cringe-worthy bridesmaid speeches, Mike and Lauren open up about their hopes to have a family, and Deena launches a clothing line.

episodes.name: Taken Pauly
episodes.overview: In the midst of the Covid-19 pandemic, Ronnie moves to L.A., Pauly introduces his Double Shot at Love girlfriend Nikki, and Lauren gets involved in Jenni and Deena's conflict with Angelina.

episodes.name: The Double Book
episodes.overview: Jenni experiences a medical mishap, Pauly rents a Las Vegas resort for the family's socially distanced vacation, and Deena shows up with Lauren and another surprise guest.

episodes.name: Single Ronnie
episodes.overview: Pauly and Vinny develop a dating show to help Ronnie find a good role model for his daughter, and the guys reach into their bags of tricks to distract Deena before Angelina's arrival.

episodes.name: Trouble Shot At Love
episodes.overview: Ronnie gets to know his dating show bachelorettes, Angelina gets a warning from her psychic grandmother, and the guys worry about how to tell Deena that Angelina's arrival is imminent.

episodes.name: Jurrasic Angelina
episodes.overview: The guys devise a backup plan to surprise Deena and an unconventional strategy for defusing Angelina's wrath, and Angelina gets pranked.

episodes.name: The Text
episodes.overview: Angelina and Deena question whether to come together on the trip, and Mike doesn't realize he's still on camera while trying to have a low-key text exchange with the guys.

episodes.name: Attack Of The Killer Raccoons
episodes.overview: The guys devise a plan to get Angelina and Deena to attend a family dinner with Nikki, but the women are hesitant to reunite.

episodes.name: Somebody's Wifey's In Town
episodes.overview: Nikki comes to dinner, Pauly gives Nikki a list of trigger words to avoid setting off Angelina and Deena, Vinny slips up, and Angelina and Deena finally talk after the wedding speech fiasco.

episodes.name: The Return of JWOWW
episodes.overview: Everyone is on edge when Jenni arrives in Las Vegas and agrees to a family dinner where she'll finally come face-to-face with Angelina.

episodes.name: The Note 2.0
episodes.overview: After an awkward family dinner with Jenni and Angelina, the guys enlist Dr. Drew to help them stage a mediation and break the tension between the ladies.

episodes.name: Calling Dr. Drew
episodes.overview: The guys call on Dr. Drew to help resolve the disputes between Angelina, Jenni and Deena, Deena learns her private chat with Mike was made public, and Mike and Lauren get exciting news.

episodes.name: The Wedding Redo
episodes.overview: As Nikki and the guys plan a redo wedding for Angelina and Chris, Uncle Nino comes in to officiate, and Vinny prepares a speech for the occasion.

episodes.name: The Speech (3)
episodes.overview: Angelina and Chris's wedding dinner takes a racy turn, Vinny wears something old to deliver his speech, and Mike and Lauren keep their pregnancy news under wraps until after the reception.

episodes.name: Ummm, Hello 2021
episodes.overview: The gang is back together and big changes are in the air. Pauly D has a new look, Vinny is looking for a new home, and when social media explodes with rumors about Angelina & Chris's marriage, Mike takes on a new alter ego -The Investigation.

episodes.name: The Party's Back
episodes.overview: Mike and Jenni step up to help when Angelina's relationship goes south, the family celebrates five years of a sober Situation, and a special guest surprises everyone.

episodes.name: The Streets Are Talking
episodes.overview: A surprise visit from Nicole makes Mike's soberversary extra special, and Jenni and The Investigation look into controversial rumors about Angelina.

episodes.name: Welcome to the Poconos
episodes.overview: Deena sets up a family trip to the Poconos, Nicole makes amends while still stirring the pot, and rumors swirling around Angelina threaten the group's vacation.

episodes.name: Mr. P
episodes.overview: Jenni has a huge announcement. But before the celebration can begin, the roommates must deal with the elephant in the room currently casting a rather large shadow over their Poconos vacation - videos of Angelina and her mystery man in Old Bridge, NJ.

episodes.name: Italian Ice
episodes.overview: Vinny suffers an unspeakable loss; Angelina confronts Jenni about the videos; and the roommates try their hand at Winter sports.

episodes.name: Guido Mania
episodes.overview: Vinny tries his hardest to get on Angelina's nerves, Zack prepares the guys for a round of guido-mania wrestling, and a surprise guest is called in to play announcer at the big match.

episodes.name: Guido Mania 2
episodes.overview: The ladies sit down to enjoy a night of Guido Mania wrestling, Angelina sticks it out to win her bet with Jenni, and Ron's girlfriend Saffire finally meets the family.

episodes.name: Guidos on Ice
episodes.overview: The girls get to know Ronnie's girlfriend, the couples face off in the first annual Bae Game, Vinny’s reunited with a long lost love, and a Jersey Shore family fun day is about to take a turn when The Investigation returns.

episodes.name: Surprise! It's a Snooki
episodes.overview: Mike shows Angelina the results of his investigation, Vinny plans a talent show, and Deena kicks off Jenni's birthday celebration, with a surprise appearance from Nicole.

episodes.name: The SS Side Piece
episodes.overview: There’s a Snooki on the loose, a couple of guidos going down in cardboard boats, and Angelina is about to make a speech. Jwoww’s birthday celebration is in full effect!

episodes.name: Worst Talent Show Ever
episodes.overview: Jwoww’s birthday celebration is on the verge of going off the rails when Snooki's alter ego Dren RSVPs. Vinny hosts the he first, and possibly the last, Annual Jersey Shore Poconos Talent Show, and tension brews between Dren and Angelina.

episodes.name: Best Birthday Ever
episodes.overview: A beef between the roomies is upstaged only by an unforgettable talent show hosted by Vinny Guadagnino, featuring an out of this world performance by Snooki, and a speech from Angelina that gives new meaning to the word “bombing.”

episodes.name: Medic
episodes.overview: With the trip coming to an end, Snooki’s left to clean up the mess made by Dren. meanwhile, Mike plans a second gender reveal even though everyone knows he’s having a boy.

episodes.name: The Meatball Day Wrap Up Special
episodes.overview: After a whirlwind season in the Pocono Mountains, the ladies of jersey Shore get together for a meatball day where they celebrate all things Season 4 with a drink or two...or ten.

episodes.name: Deliveries And Deadlines
episodes.overview: New year; new beginnings. Pauly is dusting off the turntables and finally headed back out on tour. Deena's Baby Meatball #2 is almost here, and Mike is ready to officially become “Big Daddy Sitch.” But nothing could prepare him for what happens next.

episodes.name: Snooki Vs. The Rock
episodes.overview: No longer pregnant, Deena has a meatball day with Snooki. Meanwhile, Vinny is no longer bi-coastal, Angelina is fed up, and Mike is struggling as he awaits the moment he can bring Baby Romeo home from the hospital.

episodes.name: Hollywood Shore
episodes.overview: Vinny’s realizes there’s no place like home, Mike swaps out the prosciutto for placenta, and a rumor wreaks havoc on the girls’ big West Coast trip.

episodes.name: Meatballs Don't Hike
episodes.overview: The girls’ trip to Hollywood takes a detour when they learn Vinny sold his house. But before everyone heads back, Vinny is gonna give them an LA experience they’ll always remember but may want to forget because of all the fighting between Angelina & Vinny.

episodes.name: Two Baptisms And A Pet Psychic
episodes.overview: Pauly D is headed to Jersey for the week, and it’s time for everyone to meet baby Romeo. Meanwhile, Angelina needs clarity about her marriage, so she enlists the help of pet psychic, and The Situation, gets ready for his “Blessification.”

episodes.name: The Blessification
episodes.overview: Mike feels reborn after being blessified, Angelina is feeling lost after a spiritual reading with a pet psychic, and the roomies get ready for their next family vacation

episodes.name: The Not-So-International Vacation
episodes.overview: The gang heads out for a family vacation where Mike gets a geography lesson, Jenni is in for a big surprise, and conflict comes from an unexpected place.

episodes.name: Deena's Revenge
episodes.overview: Pauly D learns how to play bingo, Angelina melts down without her luggage, Mike begins an investigation, and an alarming discovery has the roommates shook.

episodes.name: Happy Birthday, Vinny!
episodes.overview: Things get heated after the roomies realize they’ve been pranked by Deena. And Snooki arrives just in time for a floating tiki bar, Mike’s freedom party.

episodes.name: Best Party Planner Ever
episodes.overview: A tropical storm rages; Snooki and Angelina re-enact their famous fight; and the roomies party on a boat that’s also a mansion. Oh, and did we mention the sex therapist?

episodes.name: The Sexpert
episodes.overview: The Florida Keys get emotional when a sex therapist digs deep into Angelina and Chris’s relationship. Then they get messy when the meatballs create an impromptu late night talk show. And even messier when Mike finds a note from Pauly D.

episodes.name: The Lie Detector Test
episodes.overview: What truth will be uncovered when, on the last day, the roomies take on a lie detector test? Who will take gold on Wide World of Guidos? And, will Snooki ever find her wine?

episodes.name: Livin' La Vida Loca
episodes.overview: Mike learns that blondes have more fun, Pauly takes over Madison Square Garden, and group chat is lit when pictures surface of Angelina in Mexico with a man who’s not her husband.

episodes.name: Spill The Tea
episodes.overview: Angelina tells her side of the story, Jenni and Nicole bribe Deena to spill the tea, and Pauly plans a good, old-fashioned OG vacation. Meanwhile, Mike and Lauren have a difficult decision to make about Mosey.

episodes.name: Old Mike Vs. New Mike
episodes.overview: The road to El Paso takes an unexpected turn when a bunch of rumors and allegations are given to Mike. And he sends them straight to group chat, where all hell breaks loose.

episodes.name: El Paso Pt. 1
episodes.overview: The group heads to El Paso for the weekend to watch Pauly spin and join in on some line dancing. It’s love at first bite when Mike eats his first Texas tacos, but it’s anything but love between Angelina and the girls.

episodes.name: El Paso Pt. 2
episodes.overview: The party continues when DJ Pauly D takes on El Paso and the meatballs take on an owl. But it’s a FaceTime from Angelina that takes Mike over the edge.

episodes.name: Messy Mike
episodes.overview: Pauly and Vinny jet to Vegas for business and pleasure, Jenni gives a speech in her son Greyson's honor at a sensory needs awareness event, and Angelina fears the old Situation's return.

episodes.name: Mike Vs. The World
episodes.overview: The messiness finally catches up to Mike. First, in an epic showdown with Angelina and then in an emotional confrontation with Jenni.

episodes.name: The Meatball Show
episodes.overview: The squad attends Lauren's skin care launch, Ronnie returns to Jersey and opens up about his sobriety, and Nicole and Deena welcome Jerry Springer and "Amy Schumer" onto "The Meatball Show."

episodes.name: The Pool Party
episodes.overview: The guidos head to San Diego for a family vacation, but before the fun can begin there’s a lot that needs to be settled. Will the trip be over before it even begins?

episodes.name: It's Fine, I Work Here.
episodes.overview: The beef is finally squashed. But just when you think it’s all good, the tension ramps back up… Meanwhile, the “dirty stay outs” take over San Diego.

episodes.name: Lola The Bunny
episodes.overview: Easter Sunday: Jersey Shore style. Lola the Bunny returns, Angelina and Snooki wreak havoc at a winery, and the roommates enjoy an old-fashioned night out on the boardwalk. The only thing standing in the way of a good time is the beef between Mike & Deena.

episodes.name: Dren
episodes.overview: Dren (n): Snooki’s alter ego. Pauly and Nikki arrive, and the roommates meet the local wildlife. But the lions and tigers and bears got nothing on Snooki when Dren takes over on Nikki’s birthday.

episodes.name: The Staten Island Notebook
episodes.overview: Dren continues her attack on San Diego. Something is going on between Angelina and Vinny. And, when the roommates take a trip to San Diego’s Little Italy, they’re surprised to find the ultimate Guido waiting for them - Uncle Nino.

episodes.name: Wild ‘N Out: Jersey Style
episodes.overview: Deena’s “Family Fun Day” has Angelina struggling in the wake of her failed marriage. Jenni lands in the emergency room. And Nick Cannon and Justina Valentine lead the squad in an impromptu game of “Wild ‘N Out.” May the funniest guido win!

episodes.name: Knock Knock! Who’s There?
episodes.overview: Water turns into wine and in the blink of an eye, it’s pure chaos between Pauly, Nikki, and Angelina.

episodes.name: Another Day, Another Crisis
episodes.overview: Deena wonders if the previous night's showdown was all a prank, while the rest of the roomies wonder how to move forward; Vinny plans a day in his honor.

episodes.name: VIN DAY
episodes.overview: Vinny throws an epic party on the last night of the family vacation, filled with carbs, strip clubs and a late night rendezvous no one saw coming.

episodes.name: Reunion Part 1
episodes.overview: TV’s greatest Italian family returns to the reunion stage and they’re not holding back… is Angeliners finally divorced? Is old Sitch gone forever? Tacos and dramers are on the menu in Part 1 of the Jersey Shore: Family Vacation reunion!

episodes.name: Reunion Part 2
episodes.overview: Your favorite roommates aren’t done yet! Vinny and Angelina get spicy, the Meatballs embrace their wild side, and tensions get so hot one roommate leaves to cool off. The party continues tonight with Part 2 of the Jersey Shore reunion!

episodes.name: Where's the Charcuterie?
episodes.overview: The roommates rally around Mike as he says goodbye to his beloved dog, Mosey. Deena’s on edge because Angelina’s been hanging out with her brother-in-law. And the fam gets a big surprise when they hit the Shore for DJ Pauly D’s gig at Headliners.

episodes.name: Sliding Into DMs
episodes.overview: Snooki turns Deena, Angelina and JWoww into a cheer squad. Mike channels Rocky as he trains for the Super Hole 3 Corn Hole Championships, but Angelina inadvertently jeopardizes his chance for the win. And the fam heads south for the big event.

episodes.name: Lake Jersey
episodes.overview: Just an ordinary day at the lake, filled with boating, drinking, fighting, lap dancing…and a revelation that leaves the roomies speechless.

episodes.name: Life Of A Cornstar
episodes.overview: What's next for Angelina after revealing her true feelings for Vinny? And, in the words of Pauly D, a game of truth or dare gets “Awkward." Plus, the cornhole finals are here and The Situation is ready for Jay Cutler.

episodes.name: Get Your Sack In The Hole
episodes.overview: Mike wants to win it all, Prickly Elder wants to go to bed, Snooki wants to start a fire, and Angelina wants Vinny. But what does Vinny want?

episodes.name: Messy Mawmas
episodes.overview: Vinny invites Angelina to his apartment… is it a date? Nicole invites the girls to California for a business trip/wild weekend in wine country, and the Keto Guido is invited to dance with the stars.

episodes.name: Skoal!
episodes.overview: On the eve of the Dancing with the Stars premiere, Pauly and Mike travel to LA to support Vinny. Meanwhile, a girls’ weekend in wine country goes off the rails when Meatball Merlot meets a Danish beer festival.

episodes.name: Dancing With The Chooch
episodes.overview: Vinny dances, Mike makes some questionable fashion choices, and the upcoming family vacation to New Orleans is about to be taken over by beef between Angelina and Mike.

episodes.name: What A Waste Of Cake!
episodes.overview: The guidos come marching into New Orleans for a family vacation. The dirty stayouts are bringing a lot of wine, and Mike and Angelina are bringing a lot of baggage and beef.

episodes.name: Operation Mike Drop
episodes.overview: Mike continues his battle with Angelina over their Twitter war, meanwhile Pauly and Vinny hatch a plan to give Mike the gender reveal of his dreams: 10,000 ft in the air. The only problem is making sure Lauren doesn’t find out before he jumps.

episodes.name: F.F.D. 2
episodes.overview: Deena’s jazz night with costumes is only outdone when she plans another Family Fun Day with matching shirts. Plus, Angelina invites her new boyfriend on vacation, but will her Twitter beef with Mike ruin her man’s introduction to the family?

episodes.name: Divorce Party
episodes.overview: Angelina’s new man arrives just in time for her divorce party. Snooki burns Ang’s wedding dress. Pauly takes everyone to the hauntedest house ever. And Deena makes it clear she’s not afraid of JWOWW.

episodes.name: Birthday Party
episodes.overview: The Dirty Stay Outs give Angelina’s new man quite the Jersey Shore initiation. It’s Vinny’s birthday, and he’s ready for his long overdue party. But it looks like he might be disappointed yet again.

episodes.name: Engagement Party
episodes.overview: The roommates are shocked when Vinny’s birthday party unexpectedly turns into Angelina’s engagement party. But what’s even more unexpected is what happens after Angelina says yes.

episodes.name: The Hangover
episodes.overview: The aftermath of Angelina's surprise engagement leaves her and Jenni at odds; Mike The Mediation steps in, but it backfires.

episodes.name: Reunion (1)
episodes.overview: The Jersey Shore Family is back to break down another epic vacation. The shoremates break down all the big moments from this season and Angelina unexpectedly sounds off on her roommates. We love reunions this time of year!

episodes.name: Reunion (2)
episodes.overview: Vinny and Angelina get spicy; the Meatballs embrace their wild side; tensions get so hot one roommate leaves to cool off; the party continues tonight with part two of the reunion.

episodes.name: Deena's All Star Family Fun Dinner
episodes.overview: Deena invites Mike, Snooki and Jwoww to her house for dinner; this isn't just any dinner, this is a family fun dinner; there will be food, games and in-depth discussions.

episodes.name: Remember Me?
episodes.overview: Since the Jersey Shore squad started taking family vacations, there have been 14 trips and a lifetime of memories. But throughout their adventures, they have always felt like something was missing. Now that’s all about to change with one sweet return.

episodes.name: Code Word: Lasagna
episodes.overview: The roommates are in for a shocking surprise as Sammi Sweetheart returns after 11 long years.

episodes.name: Just Like Old Times
episodes.overview: Sammi's making up for lost time, catching up with her old roomies, and figuring out the new dynamics of the group; there's still a lot of unsettled business between Angelina, Deena, Jenni, and Nicole.

episodes.name: The Mothership
episodes.overview: The squad heads to the mountains, but something strange in the sky disrupts their fun.

episodes.name: The Sweetest Birthday
episodes.overview: Pauly D has the meatballs melting down. A birthday party for Sammi has Vinny feeling a little salty. And a knock on the door has everyone on edge.

episodes.name: Meatball Stakeout
episodes.overview: A surprise visitor shows up in the Poconos, the meatballs and Sammi devise a plan, and the roomies head to Atlantic City to watch Pauly spin; the trip has an unexpected twist when DNA results are revealed.

episodes.name: Charcuterie Party
episodes.overview: The guidos take over Atlantic City, and Pauly reconnects with an old friend; but the fun stops when Snooki's charcuterie party takes a turn for drama.

episodes.name: Margarita Problems!
episodes.overview: Mike starts an investigation on the whereabouts of Angelina’s biological father and continues to stir the pot as the aftermath of the charcuterie party settles in.

episodes.name: Fasten Your Seatbelt
episodes.overview: Deena’s day 1 agenda for the family fun trip includes family photos, margaritas, and a group dinner. Angelina and Mike have a sit down to talk things through.

episodes.name: Sammi’s New Man
episodes.overview: Pauly breaks down Guido fashion, Vinny has an unexpected guest, Deena and Angelina try to clear the air. And, Sammi’s boyfriend is coming to town to meet the roomies for the very first time.

episodes.name: Strip Steak
episodes.overview: Sammi’s new man has arrived, and the roomies are putting him through the ringer. The gang goes for an adventure & heads to one of their favorite places, the strip club. Meanwhile, after two long years, an old roommate is preparing for a visit to Orlando.

episodes.name: Deena Makes A Friend
episodes.overview: The Dirty Stay Outs take over the strip club, and Deena makes a new friend. For the first time in two years, Ronnie heads to Orlando to make amends.

episodes.name: Frozen Pizza And Margaritas
episodes.overview: Ronnie makes amends, and the roommates speak their piece. Meanwhile, the Angelina and Jenni dramers has Snooki stress eating and hightailing to the bar.

episodes.name: Tequila and Theories
episodes.overview: Mike continues to search for Angelina's dad; the dirty stay outs wreak havoc on Orlando, the gang has a lot of theories to unpack.

episodes.name: Dirty Try Out
episodes.overview: MVP learns the truth about the earth; Sammi tries to be a dirty stay out; Angelina needs answers from Mike.

episodes.name: Just Flip the Table
episodes.overview: The trip comes to an end; the Situation may not get out of Orlando alive; Angelina hopes to find her father.

episodes.name: Reunion (1)
episodes.overview: The family is back to redeem their biggest vacation fails and spill major shore secrets; a surprise guest leaves the meatballs kicking and screaming.

episodes.name: Reunion (2)
episodes.overview: The family reunion fun day continues, as margaritas are mixed, tables are flipped, and a roommate takes a twirl on the stripper pole.

episodes.name: Paparazzi, Poppas, and Publications
episodes.overview: Mike throws a party (for himself) and the roomies have no clue why; meanwhile an emotional journey for Angelina finally comes to an end as she meets her biological father for the very first time.

episodes.name: Reality Check
episodes.overview: While Mike throws a party for the release of his tell-all memoir, the situations reveal some shocking revelations that leave the gang gutted and speechless; Angelina's emotional reunion with her father might be too good to be true.

episodes.name: Snooki Night
episodes.overview: Snooki night turns into a girl's night that turns into Mike escaping to Vegas for a guy's night with MVP; Jenni and Sammi check in on Angelina and things get a little complicated; the gang gets an unexpected call from the mayor of Atlantic City.

episodes.name: Jersey Shore Day
episodes.overview: A getaway to Atlantic City gets sexy when Vinny strips, family dinner heats up when juicy secrets are revealed, and Angelina has some choice words for Sammi. Plus, the Mayor of Atlantic City honors the gang with their very own holiday.

episodes.name: Straight to Seaside!
episodes.overview: The family heads back to their old stomping grounds for a fun day of reminiscing; Mike and Nicole engage in a very Jersey debate; Angelina and Sammi aren't seeing eye to eye.

episodes.name: Jets Day
episodes.overview: The squad takes over MetLife stadium for an epic New York Jets game, Lauren enlists Pauly to help share some exciting news with Mike, and Snooki is praying holy water can stop the fighting between Angelina and Sammi.

episodes.name: Family Meeting
episodes.overview: Snooki invites the squad to Nashville, and Mike suggests inviting Ron on the trip. The only issue…Ron and Sammi haven’t been in the same room in over 10 years! Cue the family meeting.

episodes.name: Rhinestone Cowboy
episodes.overview: The gang is Nashville bound, and Snooki is ready to expand her business. Mike is blending in with the locals...sort of. Sammi anxiously awaits the arrival of Angelina and the return of her roomie-turned-ex, Ron.

episodes.name: Music City Meatballs
episodes.overview: The meatballs take over Nashville by pontoon and bull. The Situation eats too much food. The roomies wonder how Angelina’s arrival will affect the energy of the trip. Ron’s arrival continues to loom over Sam.

episodes.name: Sam And Ron
episodes.overview: Tensions build between Angelina and Sammi. Ronnie’s long awaited arrival sparks emotions from his roommates when he joins them in Nashville. Sammi and Ron reunite for the first time in almost a decade.

episodes.name: Jersey Hot Chicken Challenge
episodes.overview: Ronnie and Sammi's reunion has the awkwardness at an all-time high. Pauly's plan to break the tension has the roomies eating hot chicken. Vinny puts his foot in his mouth. Tension continues to build between Angelina and Sammi as the Nashville trip winds down.

episodes.name: Are You Friends With Her?
episodes.overview: Deena takes a back seat from trip planning when the guys plan the family vacation to Tucson. But after Sammi takes part in a viral Tik Tok, the serene vacation begins to take a dramatic turn.

episodes.name: Jersey Shore Fan Club?
episodes.overview: Tucson takes a turn when a Jersey Shore fan club leaks Angelina's DM's. Things come to a head between Angelina and Sammi, and there's only one man to stop it: The Situation.

episodes.name: Ronnie, Sammi And Justin
episodes.overview: Mike makes an emergency call to Thomaste when the beef between Sammi and Angelina begins to boil. Ronnie makes his way to Tucson for another family vacation with the roomies and faces Sammi and Justin.

episodes.name: OG NIGHT
episodes.overview: The squad takes it back to 2009. Pauly has a prank in mind. Mike wants to write a note. What could go wrong?

episodes.name: Happy Birthday Snooki!
episodes.overview: As the trip comes to an end, RSVP rides into old Tucson to take on some cowboys and save a damsel in distress during the most epic gender reveal.

episodes.name: Reunion (1)
episodes.overview: The shoremates return to break down the long-awaited Sammi and Ron reunion, Mike goes for a second bite of Nashville hot chicken, and we find out if the Angelina and Sammi truce is still on in Part 1 of the Jersey Shore Family Vacation Reunion!

episodes.name: Reunion (2)
episodes.overview: The shoremates go full toddler, Nicole primal releases, and the Nashville hot chicken claims another victim; an iconic Jersey Shore moment gets a spaghetti western twist.

episodes.name: The Meatball Party
episodes.overview: Sammi takes a huge step. Vinny opens up about mental health. Nicole looks for answers. And Angelina and Mike bring extra beef to the meatball party.

episodes.name: Pauly's New House
episodes.overview: Finding out who win the first annual meatball competition; the gang is invited to Las Vegas for the big game and to stay at Pauly's new house.

episodes.name: The Bunker
episodes.overview: The first night out in Vegas has Jwoww spinning and the meatballs get ready for the apocalypse; in Jersey, Angelina and 2.0 clear the air; in Los Angeles, Ronnie gives back at Lamar Odom's rehab facility.

episodes.name: The Meme
episodes.overview: The guidos can't handle the bunker or the truth about the big game; tensions between Jenni and Vinny heat up after Vinny posts a meme.

episodes.name: Sue Joey
episodes.overview: Snooki takes a huge step in the search of her biological parents. Pauly’s “big game” is finally here. Things get heated off the field when a fight breaks out in the stands.

episodes.name: What Happens In Vegas...
episodes.overview: As the Las Vegas trip comes to an end, the fireworks between Angelina and Nicole continue. Will the squad make it out of Vegas unscathed? And will Pauly’s latest prank go down in the books as a success or a bust?

episodes.name: The Feast of Peace
episodes.overview: Jenni opens up like never before; Mike and Lauren have a close call; with the beef between Angelina and Nicole looming large, it's time for the Feast of Peace.

episodes.name: A Telenovela
episodes.overview: JWOWW's feast of peace is not going as planned; Pauly teaches Nikki the difference between rigatoni and linguini; Mike organizes the next family getaway, but he doesn't know if the baby will arrive before the trip.

episodes.name: The Big Apple
episodes.overview: It's baby number 3 time for Mike and Lauren; Sammi continues her IVF journey; the rest of the gang takeover the Big Apple on a double-decker and the last stop is Vinny's standup show.
